title: Giant
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Giant

Giant may refer to:

Monsters[edit | edit source]

  • Of the giant race:
    • Black Knight Titan
    • Cyclops
    • Fire giant
    • Giant Champion
    • Glod
    • Hill Giant
    • Ice giant
    • Moss giant, and its guardian counterpart.
    • Obor
    • Bryophyta
    • Reanimated giant, summoned with an ensouled giant head and the Reanimate Giant spell.
  • Other monsters:
    • Angry giant rat
    • Giant bat
    • Giant crypt rat
    • Giant crypt spider
    • Giant eagle
    • Giant frog
    • Giant lobster, fought during The Slug Menace quest.
    • Giant lobster, fought during the Ghosts Ahoy quest.
    • Giant Mole
    • Giant mosquito
    • Giant rat
    • Giant Roc
    • Giant rockslug
    • Giant rock crab
    • Giant scarab
    • Giant Sea Snake
    • Giant skeleton, found in Tarn's Lair.
    • Giant skeleton, found in the Shadow Dungeon.
    • Giant snail
    • Giant spider

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Rag and Bone Man I bones:
    • Giant rat bone, and its polished version.
    • Giant bat wing, and its polished version.
    • Fire giant bone, and its polished version.
    • Ice giant ribs, and its polished version.
    • Moss giant bone, and its polished version.
  • Giant carp, an item used in the Fishing Contest quest.
  • Giant Dwarf, a portrait.
  • Giant key, dropped by Obor.
  • Giant pen, an item used in the Throne of Miscellania quest.
  • Giant nib, an item used in the Throne of Miscellania quest.
  • Giant present, an item obtained from Christmas events.
  • Giant pouch, an item used in Runecraft.
  • Hill giant club, dropped by Obor.

Other[edit | edit source]

  • The Giant Dwarf, a quest.
  • Giant squirrel, a pet.
  • Moss Giant Island, a location.
